@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_xsvolt(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = 0.12
    tmp = wp.sin(((tmp + 0.49 / v0 + 0.46) * 0.87))
    v2 = 0.95
    v0 = (((v2 + 0.98 / v0 + 0.38) - wp.exp(tmp + 0.76)) / (wp.exp(v1 + 0.73) / wp.abs(v2 + 0.77)))
    v2 = (tmp / wp.cos((v0 + 0.38 + v2 + 0.44)))
    data[tid] = v0
